# 📌 Pinterest Clone (Full Stack Project)

A full-stack Pinterest-inspired web application where users can create, view, like, and manage image posts (pins).

Built using **Node.js, Express, MongoDB, EJS**, and modern UI practices.

---

## 🚀 Features

### 🔐 Authentication
- User Registration & Login
- Secure authentication using Passport.js
- Session-based login system
- Flash messages for error handling

---

### 👤 User Profile
- View personal profile
- Upload profile image
- See all your created posts

---

### 📌 Posts (Pins)
- Create new posts with image upload
- View posts in profile & feed
- Open single post page
- Download images

---

### 🗑 Post Management
- Delete your own posts
- Protected routes (only owner can delete)

---

### ❤️ Interaction
- Like / Unlike posts
- View posts from other users

---

### 👥 Public Profiles
- Visit other users' profiles
- See their posts

---

### 🔍 Search
- Search users by username
- Instant redirect to profile

---

### 🎨 UI/UX Features
- Responsive design (Tailwind CSS)
- Image preview before upload
- Loading buttons & validation
- Show/Hide password 👁
- Confirm password validation (live match)
- Clean modern UI

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** EJS, Tailwind CSS
- **Backend:** Node.js, Express.js
- **Database:** MongoDB (Mongoose)
- **Authentication:** Passport.js
- **File Upload:** Multer

---

