## ⚙️ Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/pinterest-clone.git
cd pinterest-clone
npm install

🔑 Environment Variables
Create a .env file in root:

MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
SESSION_SECRET=your_secret_key


▶️ Run the Project
npm start

Open in browser:

http://localhost:3000

